\lang english
6.9 Media Loss Reporting
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard

\lang english
All County Personnel shall report the loss,
 theft,
 or suspected compromise of County media immediately upon discovery.
 Reports shall be initiated through the incident identification and reporting channels established in 
\series bold
Policy 
