caps "false"
noprefix "false"
nolink "false"

\end_inset


\series default
 (Identification and Reporting Procedures),
 which governs the internal reporting clock and CJIS notification mechanics for media-involved incidents.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
\lang english
CJI Media
\series default
:
 The loss,
 theft,
 or suspected compromise of any County media containing Criminal Justice Information (CJI) shall be reported no later than one (1) hour after discovery,
 consistent with CJIS Security Policy v6.0 IR-6 Part (a) and 
\series bold
Policy 
